'''Hanoi Fate''' is a competitive League of Legends team based in Vietnam. 

The team currently competes under the name BanhMiMinhNhat Fate in representation of their title sponsors, [https://www.facebook.com/BanhmiMasterchef/ Minh Nhat Masterchef's Bread].

